THIRD-PARTY NOTICES

This software uses the following third-party services and components:

1. Claude API by Anthropic (https://anthropic.com)
   - Used for AI inference via the Messages API
   - OAuth authentication uses Anthropic's public OAuth endpoints
   - The OAuth client_id (9d1c250a-e61b-44d9-88ed-5944d1962f5e) is a public
     identifier from the open-source Claude Code npm package
   - No proprietary Anthropic source code is included in this project

2. Apple iOS Frameworks
   - AuthenticationServices (ASWebAuthenticationSession for OAuth)
   - CryptoKit (SHA256 for PKCE)
   - Security (Keychain for token storage)
   - JavaScriptCore (JavaScript engine for node/npm)
   - Compression (gzip decompression for npm packages)
   - Network (NWListener, not currently used)

3. npm Registry (https://registry.npmjs.org)
   - Package metadata and tarballs downloaded at user's request
   - No npm Inc. code is bundled in the application

4. GitHub Actions
   - CI/CD pipeline for building and packaging the IPA
   - Uses actions/checkout, actions/cache, actions/upload-artifact

This software is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or associated with
Anthropic, Apple, npm Inc., or GitHub. "Claude" is a trademark of Anthropic.
